General.Name: Truecaller AB Series B
General.Description: Truecaller AB (publ), through its subsidiary, True Software Scandinavia AB, operates a communication platform for verifying contacts and blocking unwanted communication for individuals and businesses worldwide. It enables safe and relevant conversations between people and for businesses to connect with consumers. The company was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

6.Title: Global Chief Product Officer & MD of Truecaller India
